essions with metadata\n- [ ] `memory_context` returns token-budgeted context markdown\n- [ ] All tools visible in MCP tool discovery (`.claude/settings.local.json`)\n- [ ] Error handling: graceful failures with descriptive messages\n- [ ] Tools documented in CLAUDE.md MCP tools table\n\n## Implementation Notes\n- Build as a FastMCP plugin in `docker/trent/mcp/plugins/memory.py` (extend Task 013 file)\n- Reuse pgvector similarity search from existing RAG implementation\n- `memory_context` should use cosine similarity to find most relevant sessions, then truncate to token budget\n- Consider caching for `memory_context` (called every session start)\n\n## Files to Create/Modify\n- `docker/trent/mcp/plugins/memory.py` (extend from Task 013)\n- `docker/trent/mcp/server.py` (register new tools)\n- `CLAUDE.md` (update MCP tools table)\n- `agents.md` (update MCP tools table)\n"},"tool_output":"{\"file_path\":\"G:\\\\trent_rules\\\\.trent\\\\tasks\\\\task014_memory-mcp-tools.md\",\"success\":true}","duration":88.723,"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0172gpQoZ46weDuqnZgjvcyT","hook_event_name":"postToolUse","cursor_version":"2.5.26","workspace_roots":["/g:/trent_rules"],"user_email":"fstrent@gmail.com","transcript_path":"c:\\Users\\FSTrent\\.cursor\\projects\\g-trent-rules\\agent-transcripts\\2a12bd8d-f3eb-4225-a92c-586e34e15094\\2a12bd8d-f3eb-4225-a92c-586e34e15094.jsonl"}

